              ]
            }
          ],
          "CRITIQUE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "by compiler: it is not appropriate to assign the",
                "statistical errors derived for the cumulative yields",
                "also to the chain yields, since they were derived from",
                "charge dispersion systematics using rather crude",
                "estimates for Zp and the width parameter SIGz. Instead,",
                "an overall error should have been estimated. Whereas",
                "the difference is probably insignificant for A=107 (the",
                "Ru-107 cumulative yield is almost equal to the A=107",
                "chain yield), it is certainly significant for A=108,",
                "and particularly for A=109 where the difference is",
                "fairly large, and the statistical error is unusually",
                "small and unrealistic for the chain yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
